    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crash onto a mysterious moon and dive into the eerie depths of <i><strong>Droian</strong></i>, a sci-fi horror Metroidvania where <strong>exploration is key, and danger lurks around every corner.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/1281d7315919eaa9e932433cb6ce80db.apng?t=1749813909\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/1281d7315919eaa9e932433cb6ce80db.poster.avif?t=1749813909\" class=\"bb_img\" width=141 height=160 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crash onto a mysterious moon in <i>Droian</i>, a sci-fi horror Metroidvania where exploration and survival go hand in hand. As I.A.N, the last active bot, you’ll uncover unsettling secrets, face mechanical nightmares, and hunt for the vital Xenomorphite mineral to save humanity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With eerie pixel art inspired by Gameboy classics, cryptic lore, and multiple endings that challenge your choices, <i>Droian</i> offers a thrilling adventure filled with discovery and danger at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/f6137d1ced388ed1afadabcec6cdaa0f.poster.avif?t=1749813909\" width=404 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/f6137d1ced388ed1afadabcec6cdaa0f.webm?t=1749813909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/f6137d1ced388ed1afadabcec6cdaa0f.mp4?t=1749813909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/767dda7ce3764065650c707624303f8a.webp?t=1749813909\" width=793 height=26 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse the desolate yet eerie DMI moon, filled with secrets hidden in every corner.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysteries of Xenomorphite and help I.A.N complete his mission.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear exploration — collect items and unlock areas in your own order.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Always check your crevices&quot; - Subtle Narrative with Extensive Lore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/6197fa8fd99bb305439590fbf992c5bc.webp?t=1749813909\" width=680 height=25 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face terrifying bosses and enemies that blend flesh and machine in gruesome ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in strategic combat against creatures that challenge both skill and wit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scary and atmospheric, but challenging rather than punishing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three spine-tingling bosses and many monstrous encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sci-fi and Metroidvania fans will enjoy the balance of exploration and combat.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/2737dc8f0ed821283d4ab6c3f619c6df.poster.avif?t=1749813909\" width=404 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/2737dc8f0ed821283d4ab6c3f619c6df.webm?t=1749813909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/2737dc8f0ed821283d4ab6c3f619c6df.mp4?t=1749813909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256060/extras/15ab61395f7d01429847b8b72a4e7a33.webp?t=1749813909\" width=744 height=56 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Subtle storytelling with a lot of hidden lore for conspiracy lovers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the cryptic history of X-corps, the DMI moon, and its connection to humanity’s survival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings that make you question your choices — who is the man at the door? Did I really <i>save</i> Humanity?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for conspiracy theorists who love piecing together subtle story clues.</p></li></ul>",
